Define Group	KbdVel	V100	V25	V50	V75	V127
Define Group	BaseKey	C2	C0	C1	C3	C4
Define Group	TempoSync	Free	Sync
//	Control Surface Item	Key	Remotable Item	Scale	Mode
Map	DeviceScope		"PX7"
Map	DeviceName		Device Name
Map	PatchName		Patch Name
Map	Button C3		Select Previous Patch
Map	Button C4		Select Next Patch
// Page
Map	Button C5		Page=Main
Map	Button C6		Page=Keyboard
Map	Button C7		Page=Index
// Keyboard
Map	PageName		"Keyboard"			Keyboard	
Map	Button 1-4		KbdVel=V25			Keyboard	
